## Node name
-name barrel@127.0.0.1

## Cookie for distributed Erlang
-setcookie barrel_secret

## Enable kernel poll (improves performance on Linux)
+K true

## Async thread pool size
+A 64

## Max ports (file handles)
-env ERL_MAX_PORTS 65536

## Enable SMP
-smp auto

## Scheduler settings
+S 4:4
+SDcpu 4:4

## Memory settings
+MBas aobf
+MBlmbcs 512

## Crash dump location
-env ERL_CRASH_DUMP ./log/erl_crash.dump
